0.5.0
	- Not backwards compatible!
	- Tasks are defined differently (via module instead of inheritance).
	- Some configuration options have changed or removed completely.
	- Configuration options are specified differently as according to ConfigurationDsl v0.3.0.
	- Removed all reporting/statstics gathering code.  Use external tools if you want that functionality (.e.g. Nagios and/or Statsd)
	- Added support to run in fibered mode (requires EventMachine).

0.4.0
	- Internal Onespot release.

0.3.0
	- Internal Onespot release.

0.2.0
	- Refactored

